### Component Interactions

**Initialization Flow:**
```
orchestrator.py
    в”ңв”Җ> router/heuristic.py (or vision_router.py)
    в”ңв”Җ> embedding/text_path.py
    в”Ӯ       в”ңв”Җ> text_extractor.py (PaddleOCR)
    в”Ӯ       в””в”Җ> text_embedder.py (nomic-embed)
    в”ңв”Җ> embedding/vision_path.py
    в”Ӯ       в””в”Җ> vision_embedder.py (ColPali)
    в”ңв”Җ> storage/qdrant_backend.py (or lancedb_backend.py)
    в””в”Җ> retrieval/retriever.py
```

**Processing Flow:**
```
User вҶ’ orchestrator.process_document()
    в”ңв”Җ> router.classify(page)
    в”ңв”Җ> text_path.process_page() OR vision_path.process_page()
    в”ңв”Җ> storage.insert(embedding)
    в””в”Җ> return statistics

User вҶ’ orchestrator.query()
    в”ңв”Җ> retriever.encode_query()
    в”ңв”Җ> storage.search(query_embedding)
    в””в”Җ> return QueryResult
```

**Data Flow:**
```
PDF вҶ’ Page (numpy array)
    вҶ’ ClassificationResult (router)
    вҶ’ EmbeddingResult (text/vision path)
    вҶ’ Vector DB (storage)
    вҶ’ QueryResult (retrieval)
```

